(368, 'Revolex Extreme - Fitness To The Next Level', 'Revoflex Xtreme Home gym Great For daily Excercise Good Fitness Product Work out for many body parts', '999', '599', 'letterM', 'https://www.sportcart.in/products/2021/670/71pn9bozlsl1500.jpg'),
