(370, 'Yoga Mat - Best Quality', '* INSTANT HOME STUDIO IN ANY ROOM – Go ahead and stretch out like never before. Just unroll to transform any room in your home into your very own home studio or gym.  * Our spacious mat is large enough for any yoga pose, meditation, stretch, light cardio workout or barefoot bodyweight exercise – by yourself or with a friend            * DOUBLE-SIDED PERFORMANCE DESIGN – Sticky, textured, non-slip top provides unmatched grip and comfort. Unique, circle-pattern bottom grips and prevents the mat from sliding around. Crafted from premium, eco-friendly, non-toxic materials with no latex, odor or smell.                                                                   * Exceptional resilience allow you to keep your balance during any exercise style. Moisture resistant Technology makes the mat to be easily washed with soap and water. * Package contents :- 1 Yoga Mat   ', '1100', '649', 'letterM', 'https://www.sportcart.in/products/2020/32/215.jpg'),
