(373, 'Waist Twister', '* The magnetic acupressure waist twister to help you lose weight and stay fit. * Just a simple twisting action can have a strong effect on the abs. * Made with best quality material. * Package Contents :- 1 Waist Twister * Colour can vary', '949', '699', 'letterM', 'https://www.sportcart.in/products/2020/563/img0098.jpg'),
